Load schema for an austraits.build data compilation (excluding traits)

get_schema.Rd

Load schema for an austraits.build data compilation (excluding traits)

get_schema(
  path = system.file("support", "austraits.build_schema.yml", package =
    "austraits.build"),
  subsection = NULL
)

Arguments

path

path to schema file. By default loads version included with the package

subsection

section to load

Value

a list

Examples

{

schema <- get_schema()
}
